line_1: For then Alass! thou had'st t'engage
line_2: Is Folly not to be forgiv'n in ev'n thy Doating Age.

line_1: REclaim, rash Friend, your wild Resolves t'engage
Oft in Wild Sarra's Desert forc't t'engage
